<!-- description -->
<td>This past Easter Long weekend we had our first of hopefully what will become an annual trip back to <a href="http://www.surfjunction.com/" title="Surf Junction Campground">Surf Junction Campground</a>.
The trip was a huge success, fun was had by all, the surf was great so was the food so were the people, a good time was had by all.  
Its a three day trip and it cost $170 and that included transportation, 1.5 dinners, 2 kegs of beer, rentals, and good good times.
