<p align="left">
keep in mind here guys, <b>no refunds</b> unless you can find a replacement.  Its hard enough doing this trips without people (especially drivers) backing out at the last minute, so as a rule we do not reserve spots unless you pay (ie if your on the list and you have not paid you may get bumped for somebody with the $) or if you have paid and anything comes up and you are unable to go it is <b>your</b> responsibility to find a replacement, otherwise we can not return your money.  This may sound a bit stringent at the moment, but trust me, we have to pay for stuff in advance and we def. cannot afford for a large portion of a trip to back out, its just not doable, we have to commit to hotels, rental places, ferry reservations, and on and on... 
</p>
