<p align="left">This page chronicles the global adventures of people in the surf club. Many of the execs are well traveled, knowledgeable about foreign countries, and want to share their wavely conquests with all. However, anyone else may send in tales of victory and defeat at the hands of the ocean in far away lands, and it shall be posted here in a timely fashion.</p>
